{"tid":1528673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"作為岩岩其中一個上左校巴既學生，好想再次同各校巴司機講聲多謝","createTime":"2019-09-01T14:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T15:19:32.000Z","uid":158973,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b457a3901987da640f549c24df01e459a4b1b0","tid":1528673,"uid":158973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:44:45.000Z","msg":"今次真係唔同之前<br />\n一開始果陣已經feel到大家好徬徨<br />\n個個喺到問:吓要行兩個鐘?<br />\n仲要行行下天都黑埋，望前面終點又遠，路又唔安全<br />\n個個睇落都已經又驚又攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩沿路都keep住有校巴司機接放學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又問要唔要水食物，又準備左衫比我地換<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺車到望出去沿路有好多校巴，超級感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今鋪如果少左班校巴司機，大家個絕望感會重好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心好感激佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申發夢夢見返學放學情況"},{"pid":"dce23a50eb0425dcfab58a289357a0884219a70f","tid":1528673,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦曬巴打"},{"pid":"1433204db539a4b2af13cca14baf597fdfd704fb","tid":1528673,"uid":281159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:46:29.000Z","msg":"多謝老師送我放學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b32c1c3e4c92dc0ce74fafad654fdb9e945e7c","tid":1528673,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:47:43.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安<br />\n仆街宣明會 收皮啦 ,你地小左捐款香港市民會幫你祈禱"},{"pid":"c388fe9b49a5533a6131bf2c2cd7a36f3651cf12","tid":1528673,"uid":162590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n睇live 聽到見到好感動<br />\n全部愛香港既香港人一世平安<br />\n<br />\n好多謝咁多位爸爸媽媽接放學<br />\n真係好多謝"},{"pid":"b8892993913231267b16df451c29cb6c974ec961","tid":1528673,"uid":272587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:19:32.000Z","msg":"我愛家長"}]}